Class StructType

  • Object
    • org.apache.spark.sql.api.java.DataType
      • org.apache.spark.sql.api.java.StructType

  • public class StructType
extends DataType
    The data type representing Rows. A StructType object comprises an array of StructFields. To create an StructType, DataType.createStructType(java.util.List) or DataType.createStructType(StructField[]) should be used.
